<emphasis id="AE8B64D913A790EA2CAAF38217180154" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Lepanthes oro-lojaensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Tobar &amp; M.F.Lopez (black pentagon, one collection).
</paragraph>
